{"tid":565518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社協指精神復康服務資源極不足促增撥款","createTime":"2018-02-19T05:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T11:39:35.000Z","uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"531bda05390660533621c19064c0ddc90263460e","tid":565518,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:08:33.000Z","msg":"社區組織協會十多名代表早上到政府總部請願，要求政府在月底發表的財政預算案中，增撥資源投放在精神復康服務。協會幹事彭鴻昌表示，本港的精神復康服務資源極度不足，開支只佔本地生產總值0.22%，遠遠落後於已發展國家，要求將開支提升至佔本地生產總值0.5%，即約一百三十億元；新增的撥款可用作培訓提供精神健康服務的專職醫護人員，以及延長政府精神復康診所的診症時間。<br />\n<br />\n彭鴻昌指，不少精神病康復者的家人未必理解康復者的需要，導致難以同住，要求政府加強住宿照顧服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=993627&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D993627%26csid%3D261_341&d=NOwHBB%2FopAcSV4JlwH5FeqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=a9657b54\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=993627&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"4ac1484ef32d3cef3c062816a2e4203f4ab65f3e","tid":565518,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92a632abb72e5062a59afb4cfb5213c1be1554e","tid":565518,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:17:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">社區組織協會</span>"},{"pid":"e0c691f3e5ca478ebb7a3fa2c5afc234cb40c355","tid":565518,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a92a632abb72e5062a59afb4cfb5213c1be1554e","tid":565518,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:17:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">社區組織協會</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:18:24.000Z","msg":"何生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2359ed52fb05a9cc7f676361897e7d5dd95ddf2","tid":565518,"uid":53